      "body" : "@luke-jr you can't redefine policy opcode because people are likely to have utxos with that.\r\n\r\nand it won't make sense to create more NOPs. The use of NOPs is really limited as they can't manipulate the stack at all. For example, my most wanted code, OP_CAT, could not be done with and NOP",
